["level202010"]={id="level202010",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,115_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这种事……对不起，我没有留意过。况且它们是鸟，只要飞得高些……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202011"]={id="level202011",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,115_sad",npcImageColor="",content_langId="重鹤哥哥，你的伤严重吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202012"]={id="level202012",bodyPos="2=1161,115",offset={{0,0},{0,-150},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,116_close,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="说了好几次，您叫我重鹤便足矣……罢了，阿桃。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202013"]={id="level202013",bodyPos="2=1161,115",offset={{0,0},{0,-150},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那只妖怪并非为我而来。若要夺回药草，及时追击方是上策。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202014"]={id="level202014",bodyPos="1=115,1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,115_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我也……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202015"]={id="level202015",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="小谷主，你就留在铸剑阁，帮我们照看一下伤员吧！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202016"]={id="level202016",bodyPos="2=102,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,-80},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苒苒留在阁中，恐怕还有后患。我们将她一并带走，日落之前，定当回来向二位赔罪。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level202017"]={id="level202017",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,115_sad",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那……就交给你们了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203001"]={id="level203001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="沿着临行前都阿桃的指引，前方妖气渐浓，或是一番干戈后，它们已无心掩饰踪迹。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_xuanya",effect="",},
["level203002"]={id="level203002",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="树林的尽头是一片开阔的平崖，数只飞禽正栖息在乱石上。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203003"]={id="level203003",bodyPos="3=802",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="5,0",},
["level203004"]={id="level203004",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这就是玉叶谷闻名天下的伏龙草……百年只生一株，据说可解天下万毒。这一点微末的毒性，自然也不在话下。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="5,1",},
["level203005"]={id="level203005",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="只可惜你们目光短浅，被一道计策便骗得团团乱转，真是可笑至极！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203006"]={id="level203006",bodyPos="3=102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{147,-100}},modelldScale={60,60,85},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="开出你的条件。我们并非势不两立。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203007"]={id="level203007",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我？当然，我也有所求。有位大人怜悯我苟活至今却大仇未报，便允我前来……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203008"]={id="level203008",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我想要的，自然唯有她的命而已。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203009"]={id="level203009",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,101_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你究竟……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203010"]={id="level203010",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="饕餮妄图插手叶氏朝廷，葬送了我亲人性命的时候，有谁站出来过？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203011"]={id="level203011",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他们的尸身被扔在城楼下曝晒时，有谁怜悯过？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203012"]={id="level203012",bodyPos="3=701",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="饕餮虽死，却不是死于我的手中，今日，终于大仇得报……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203013"]={id="level203013",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,101_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="住手！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="1",},
["level203014"]={id="level203014",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="碧影猛然挥剑，却已迟了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203015"]={id="level203015",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="顷刻间烈火迸发，将鸦妖连同爪中的灵草包裹成一团火球。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level203016"]={id="level203016",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="它发出凄厉的啼叫，在火焰中皮肉寸寸焦黑，猛然张开双翼，坠向深不见底的崖下。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level204001"]={id="level204001",bodyPos="2=102,1041",offset={{0,0},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="停步，不可再追了。此处悬崖往下深不见底，已经……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_xuanya",effect="",},
["level204002"]={id="level204002",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="104_think,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你们照看好苒苒，这未必就是一条死路。就算是，也得想办法下去一试。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level204003"]={id="level204003",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="别……别去。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,苒苒",},
["level204004"]={id="level204004",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="一只手轻轻地拽了拽荆高手的衣领。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="cg2_2",effect="",},
["level204005"]={id="level204005",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他说的事，大家都明白吧？啊，除了阁主……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level204006"]={id="level204006",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那是……关于我父亲的事情。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,苒苒",},
["level204007"]={id="level204007",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……不必急于一时，先养足精神吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,叶云天",},
["level204008"]={id="level204008",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我的父亲去世前，把我留在了铸剑阁中。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,苒苒",},
