["level204010"]={id="level204010",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗯。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,碧影",},
["level204011"]={id="level204011",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他失败了，最后只留下了我。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,苒苒",},
["level204012"]={id="level204012",bodyPos="0=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我喜欢武陵山、喜欢山下的小镇……当然，小荆、云天，碧影和阁主，还有铸剑阁……全都很喜欢！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,苒苒",},
["level204013"]={id="level204013",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="她的声音渐渐低了一些。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level204014"]={id="level204014",bodyPos="3=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,100_coma",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我最快乐的时光，是和大家一起度过的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_xuanya",effect="",},
["level204015"]={id="level204015",bodyPos="3=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="所以……我相信爹爹……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level205001"]={id="level205001",bodyPos="1=115,1161",offset={{0,0},{0,-150},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你们回来啦！怎么样了？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="talkScene1",effect="",},
