["level307017"]={id="level307017",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="景象虽已不存…脑中却仿佛回想起了什么。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level307018"]={id="level307018",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…无妨，不必在意。只是头脑忽然有些昏沉而已。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["level307019"]={id="level307019",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="步履未停。不远处正是谣音镇主事之人——鹿茵的府邸。亭亭苍木立于楼台间，摇曳树影落入视线中，似有零星感召浮现。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401001"]={id="level401001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="随侍者来到府邸中苒苒所在的房间，眼前除了解毒后陷入沉睡的苒苒，还有一名面色苍白的少女，正捂着手腕坐在床边。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_night",effect="",},
["level401002"]={id="level401002",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="呼……还好有你们把苒苒送到了，我们在外头耽搁了好一会……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401003"]={id="level401003",bodyPos="2=1161,-115",offset={{0,0},{0,-150},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…谷主，下回莫要这般冲动了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401004"]={id="level401004",bodyPos="1=-115,1161",offset={{0,0},{0,-150},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="晓得啦晓得啦～不过苒苒没事就好。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401005"]={id="level401005",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="许姑娘愿意出手相救，我在此代铸剑阁谢过了，日后定当报答。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["level401006"]={id="level401006",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="没错，苒苒这回真是多亏玉叶谷几位相助！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401007"]={id="level401007",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="腕上的血已经止住了，不过看许诗葵的脸色也能知道，她此刻并不轻松。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401008"]={id="level401008",bodyPos="3=10007",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-140}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="没关系，我能感应到，苒苒的痛苦……希望她做个好梦。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401009"]={id="level401009",bodyPos="2=115,-10007",offset={{0,-140},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="辛苦阿葵了…的确，若不是苒苒，我也没有走出玉叶谷的勇气，更别说真正地看一看这方世界了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401010"]={id="level401010",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="静候在一旁的重鹤默默听着，微不可察地变了变神色。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401011"]={id="level401011",bodyPos="2=115,-10007",offset={{0,-140},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="对了阿葵，我们来了好一会儿了，怎么没见到茵姐呢？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401012"]={id="level401012",bodyPos="1=-10007,115",offset={{0,-140},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我来此地时，就未曾见过她，应是出去了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401013"]={id="level401013",bodyPos="2=115,-10007",offset={{0,-140},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="奇怪……是有什么急事么，至少见一见再离开呀……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401014"]={id="level401014",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="想再说些话时，都阿桃才后知后觉地皱了皱眉——顺着她的视线看去，是被丝丝鲜血洇染过的衣袖。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401015"]={id="level401015",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阿桃，你怎么受伤了！？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401016"]={id="level401016",bodyPos="2=115,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="可能是和刚才那几个人动手的时候不小心……没事，也不过是个小伤口。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401017"]={id="level401017",bodyPos="1=1161,115",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……自谷主同苒苒姑娘相识之后，性格倒是独立了许多。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401018"]={id="level401018",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="误以为这是一则来之不易的肯定，都阿桃听了，高兴得连带着耳朵也动了动。未曾想马上又被泼了冷水。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401019"]={id="level401019",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="若不是执意要离开玉叶谷……也不会平添如此事端。甚至耗费了许姑娘百年的灵气。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401020"]={id="level401020",bodyPos="2=115,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…………",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401021"]={id="level401021",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="觉察到都阿桃示意自己噤声的目光，重鹤也不好再多言，随后便拂袖告退，离开了房间。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401022"]={id="level401022",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,115_look",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…对不住大家，他……只是太担心我了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401023"]={id="level401023",bodyPos="2=101,-115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401024"]={id="level401024",bodyPos="1=-115,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="碧影，怎么了？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401025"]={id="level401025",bodyPos="2=101,-115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="袭击苒苒的人，究竟是谁呢……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level401026"]={id="level401026",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="低语片刻，碧影轻叹一声，还是决意问出口来。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
