["level401028"]={id="level401028",bodyPos="2=115,-101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="碧影姐姐这话是何意？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402001"]={id="level402001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="都阿桃似乎想到了什么，却有些许迟疑。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_night",effect="",},
["level402002"]={id="level402002",bodyPos="1=-115,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="玉叶谷内绝不会有人要暗害苒苒。更何况……谷内事务其实大多都是重鹤哥哥在处理，有什么异动，他应当第一时刻就知道的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402003"]={id="level402003",bodyPos="2=101,-115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="若是……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402004"]={id="level402004",bodyPos="1=-115,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="115_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="不可能的…！他、他么会做那种事呢。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="6",},
["level402005"]={id="level402005",bodyPos="1=-115,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="115_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他是对我出谷一事有所不满…但，总归还是为了我好而已……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402006"]={id="level402006",bodyPos="2=101,-115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…我们绝无猜忌之意。但，既有疑惑，至少可以先试探一番。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402007"]={id="level402007",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="虽是辩驳着，可都阿桃还是露出了不安的神情，背过身看了看许诗葵，握住了她并未受伤的那只手。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402008"]={id="level402008",bodyPos="3=10007",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-140}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阿桃……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402009"]={id="level402009",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="连你也不相信他么……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402010"]={id="level402010",bodyPos="3=115",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="好，好吧……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402011"]={id="level402011",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（当日晚）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="black",effect="",},
["level402012"]={id="level402012",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁下深夜来访，又何必匆匆离开呢？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_yewainight",effect="",},
["level402013"]={id="level402013",bodyPos="2=804,1161",offset={{0,-150},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="凭你，还留不住我。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,2,？？？",},
["level402014"]={id="level402014",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="来人身法矫健，同重鹤过招丝毫不落下风。二人一时间难分高下，追打至院落中时，对方隐隐透出欲要脱逃之势。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402015"]={id="level402015",bodyPos="1=1161,804",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="116_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="站住，你走不了！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402016"]={id="level402016",bodyPos="2=804,1161",offset={{0,-150},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（低声）嘁、能拖你这一时半刻，那小狐狸也没救兵了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,2,？？？",},
["level402017"]={id="level402017",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="随后，此人便飞身躲开了下一击，匆匆离去。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level402018"]={id="level402018",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,116_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他说的是……不好，阿桃！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403001"]={id="level403001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="天刚蒙蒙亮时，重鹤便匆匆闯入房中。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="talkScene1",effect="",},
["level403002"]={id="level403002",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阿桃怎样了？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="6",},
["level403003"]={id="level403003",bodyPos="2=101,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="昨夜那群袭击苒苒的人又来了，谷主为了保护苒苒……受了些伤，现下许姑娘正为她医治。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403004"]={id="level403004",bodyPos="1=1161,101",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="袭击苒苒…？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403005"]={id="level403005",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="有些蹊跷地，重鹤没有继续追问都阿桃的情况，反倒谈起袭击苒苒一事。这样的做法似乎暗暗印证了碧影的猜想。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403006"]={id="level403006",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,116_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="铸剑阁诸多能人异士…居然还需要谷主来保护她？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403007"]={id="level403007",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,116_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…我要见谷主。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403008"]={id="level403008",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他不愿再多说，径直越过众人，走向都阿桃所在的房间。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403009"]={id="level403009",bodyPos="1=-115,10007",offset={{0,0},{0,-140},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="115_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="咳咳……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403010"]={id="level403010",bodyPos="2=10007,-115",offset={{0,0},{0,-140},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,70,60},bodyAniList={},expression="115_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阿桃…谷主身体无恙，不必太过担心。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403011"]={id="level403011",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="多谢许姑娘相助。不过…此地果然还是不太安全。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403012"]={id="level403012",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="说罢，他的视线扫过门外几人。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403013"]={id="level403013",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…谷主可曾看清是何人来犯？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403014"]={id="level403014",bodyPos="2=115,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗯，那些人的妖气……和此前袭击苒苒的人确实是相似的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403015"]={id="level403015",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="眼见都阿桃也这么说，重鹤的神色终于透出一丝并不寻常的凝重。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403016"]={id="level403016",bodyPos="2=115,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="怎么了，哥哥，你知道他们是谁吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403017"]={id="level403017",bodyPos="1=1161,115",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="并非如此。只是昨夜交过手罢了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403018"]={id="level403018",bodyPos="1=1161,115",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="谷主受了伤，还是先好好休息吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403019"]={id="level403019",bodyPos="2=115,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_sad,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="重鹤哥哥……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level403020"]={id="level403020",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="再想问些什么，却没有机会了。都阿桃望着重鹤快步离开的背影，欲言又止。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404001"]={id="level404001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="谣音镇外，树下一隅。身受重伤的羽妖匍匐在地。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_qingqiuxu",effect="",},
["level404002"]={id="level404002",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,100,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,116_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="没有我的命令私自行动，你们应当知晓下场会如何。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404003"]={id="level404003",bodyPos="2=700,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,100,60},bodyAniList={},expression="116_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="咳、咳咳……地尊息怒…！我等深知谷主在地尊心中地位，又怎会对谷主出手？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404004"]={id="level404004",bodyPos="2=700,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,100,60},bodyAniList={},expression="116_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="上回也是如此，纵使再恨那只饕餮……谷主现身之时，我等便立刻退走了…！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404005"]={id="level404005",bodyPos="1=1161,700",offset={{0,-150},{0,100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,100,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404006"]={id="level404006",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="比起羽妖无关痛痒的答复，显然有更值得注意之事——重鹤背过身去，不远处的几簇杂草，似有细碎的响动。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404007"]={id="level404007",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……铸剑阁的诸位，倒也不必隐藏了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404008"]={id="level404008",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="话音刚落，一柄利刃便杀至眼前——",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404009"]={id="level404009",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="狗贼！还真是你个**——",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404010"]={id="level404010",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="几人合围之下，重鹤渐渐不敌，被逼至死角。待到此时，都阿桃才缓缓上前。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404011"]={id="level404011",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="有意忽视了都阿桃复杂的神情，重鹤只是淡淡开口：",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404012"]={id="level404012",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="先前真是小瞧诸位了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level404013"]={id="level404013",bodyPos="3=1161",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,-150}},modelldScale={60,60,70},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,116_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="不过我还是有些好奇，几位如何猜到是在下命人追杀苒苒姑娘的呢？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405001"]={id="level405001",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="住口！你没脸叫苒苒的名字！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_qingqiuxu",effect="",},
["level405002"]={id="level405002",bodyPos="2=101,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="104_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……阁下城府深密。唯一能使你破除伪装的，恐怕也只有谷主了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405003"]={id="level405003",bodyPos="2=101,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="104_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苒苒同谷主交好，受她影响，谷主才有了离开玉叶谷游历的念头。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405004"]={id="level405004",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{-147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁下虽一心想要保护谷主，但常年将她留在谷中……算了，这是玉叶谷内部之事，我不好多嘴。只是，总归不应迁怒于苒苒。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405005"]={id="level405005",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{-147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="玉叶谷中，知晓苒苒饕餮后裔身份的不过寥寥数人。然而以阁下对玉叶谷的掌控，要得知这一点的确易如反掌。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405006"]={id="level405006",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{-147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="最后，再将这些告知你手下的羽族妖兽，让它们去追杀苒苒，也就顺理成章了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405007"]={id="level405007",bodyPos="2=115,-102",offset={{-147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你利用众多妖族对饕餮一族的恨意，怂恿它们去袭击苒苒……！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405008"]={id="level405008",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="都阿桃的声音愈发小下去，像是不愿接受这个事实一般。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405009"]={id="level405009",bodyPos="2=115,1161",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,115_look,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="怎么偏偏是你呢……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405010"]={id="level405010",bodyPos="1=1161,115",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="谷主……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405011"]={id="level405011",bodyPos="1=1161,115",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…若这些都是谷主独自想出来的主意，那还真是一件值得高兴的事。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405012"]={id="level405012",bodyPos="1=1161,115",offset={{0,-150},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="不过，即便我不告知，它们在将来某天知道了真相，那个女孩怕是也会有相同的遭遇吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level405013"]={id="level405013",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你——！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
