["guide101023"]={id="guide101023",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="您不认识我并不出奇，但总该认识苒苒的……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101024"]={id="guide101024",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="…碧影本是上任阁主，也就是您的师尊“琉”所铸神剑中的剑灵。在十年前的极渊之战中得以化形入世。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101025"]={id="guide101025",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="您正是在那次战争后陷入了昏迷，直至今日……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101026"]={id="guide101026",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="“阁主”……？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide101027"]={id="guide101027",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主不但不记得苒苒，连铸剑阁也不记得了……这要怎么医，不会只能拿苒苒的锤子敲敲阁主的脑袋了吧？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101028"]={id="guide101028",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="此处乃铸剑阁，云麓之上的神兵利器，无不是出自我们这里，出自阁主之手的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guidechoice101004"]={id="guidechoice101004",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="铸造兵器……？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101029"]={id="guide101029",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（提及此事时，不知为何，胸中涌起一阵悸动。是温暖吗？是苦涩吗？多得令人来不及思考的情绪涌了上来，想要抓住时，却又从指中飘散。）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide101030"]={id="guide101030",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（这一定是件对自己而言，非常非常重要，重要到在丧失了一切的现在，也不愿遗落的事情……）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide101031"]={id="guide101031",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="碧影……阁主看来是真的都不记得了……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101032"]={id="guide101032",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="但不妨事，阁主昏迷前那么厉害，想必睡了十年……也没关系的！带你到阁中走走看看，说不定就能记起来什么了！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101033"]={id="guide101033",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="一只温暖的手径直握了上来。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide101034"]={id="guide101034",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苒苒，小心些——",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide102001"]={id="guide102001",bodyPos="1=-100,101=0.8",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="怎样？有没有觉得……有一点点熟悉？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide102002"]={id="guide102002",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="空气中浮动着陈旧的灰尘气味。这间厅堂似乎已在岁月中沉寂多年，直到今日再度重启。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide102003"]={id="guide102003",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苒苒经常在外面的草地上和你玩捉迷藏哦！阁主快看，这张柜台的桌腿上还刻着我的画……哎呀，怎么这么多灰！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide102004"]={id="guide102004",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="cg_ranran",effect="",},
["guide102005"]={id="guide102005",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（这是什么时候的事呢……）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="*",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide102006"]={id="guide102006",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="有些日子没来，桌上都积了这么多尘啊……一定是小荆收拾到一半就偷偷跑出去玩啦！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide102007"]={id="guide102007",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……说起来，上月底自告奋勇要来清理的人是……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide102008"]={id="guide102008",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="是谁？哈哈哈哈哈，有这回事吗，肯定不是我……吧……？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103001"]={id="guide103001",bodyPos="2=101,-100=0.8",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗯，这样看来，铸剑阁也整洁了许多。苒苒，去将对外营业的木牌挂起来吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guidechoice103001"]={id="guidechoice103001",bodyPos="",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……现在？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103002"]={id="guide103002",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="话音刚落，苒苒可怜兮兮地看了过来。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103003"]={id="guide103003",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主，你醒来得真是太及时了……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103004"]={id="guide103004",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="自阁主陷入昏迷后，我们对外只说是因为您身体不适，故而暂且闭门，也谢绝见客。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103005"]={id="guide103005",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="铸剑阁原本亦有许多人脉与财力积累。但毕竟十年之中，我们几乎没有进账。这是账簿，请您过目。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103006"]={id="guide103006",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="上面密布着娟秀字迹,只不过翻过一页又一页，所录事项似乎尽是……有出无入。看起来十分凄凉。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103007"]={id="guide103007",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="也就是说，咱们真的快没钱啦！还好阁主醒了，再过个三两月，大家估计都要吃不起饭了……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103008"]={id="guide103008",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="所以，阁主你得赶紧把铸剑阁经营起来……不然除了碧影，大家都要饿死啦！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guidechoice103008_1"]={id="guidechoice103008_1",bodyPos="",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那还有我的口粮吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guidechoice103008_2"]={id="guidechoice103008_2",bodyPos="",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="没有别的挣钱方式吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103009"]={id="guide103009",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="请您放心，碧影正在向村民学习如何种植蔬菜，铸剑阁旁的那块菜地，近日长势十分喜人。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103010"]={id="guide103010",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="有的有的，我正在训练小荆——也是我们铸剑阁的人，练习胸口碎大石好去卖艺——",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103011"]={id="guide103011",bodyPos="2=101,-100=0.7",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="说回正题，若要开张，我们便该准备些货物。老阁主将百兵图录编纂为《天工谱》，虽经动乱散佚，但仍有一卷录有长剑浇铸之法的图纸存在阁中，足以一用。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103012"]={id="guide103012",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="请不要忧虑，也无需迷茫，即便失去记忆也无妨，我……碧影剑的剑魂，对您仍感到无比的亲近。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide103013"]={id="guide103013",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,101_smile,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="您曾创造出无数与我相似的“有心之器”。这必定是因为，您的心中，便蕴藏着无限的情感与可能性……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide104001"]={id="guide104001",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="啊，这么快就有客人来了？看来十年过去，我们铸剑阁还是威名不减嘛！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide104002"]={id="guide104002",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="您好您好！快请进！想要买点什么呢？这里应有尽有哦！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide104003"]={id="guide104003",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide104004"]={id="guide104004",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……他说他只是路过，瞧见这儿开着门，就想讨碗水喝……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide104005"]={id="guide104005",bodyPos="2=101,-100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guidechoice104001"]={id="guidechoice104001",bodyPos="",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（没办法，那就只能靠我了！）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide104006"]={id="guide104006",bodyPos="0=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="请看这把刚刚铸好的铁剑。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide104007"]={id="guide104007",bodyPos="0=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="常在山中行走，怎能没有一把武器护身？敝店承诺卖出去的每把兵器，都有三年保修期！您瞧这剑锋……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide104008"]={id="guide104008",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="吹毛立断！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide104009"]={id="guide104009",bodyPos="0=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗯嗯，不错不错，您再看这剑格——",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide104010"]={id="guide104010",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="还刻了非常好看的花纹呢！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105001"]={id="guide105001",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="方才看阁主铸剑的手法，倒是完全没有生疏。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide105002"]={id="guide105002",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主虽然脑袋不记得，但手还记得呢。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105003"]={id="guide105003",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这样一来，我近日就去将铸剑阁恢复经营的消息广布开，以便正式开门迎客。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105004"]={id="guide105004",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这里还有些图纸，阁主不妨再熟悉熟悉。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105005"]={id="guide105005",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主再做个锤子好了，要是失败了也没关系，苒苒可以用它来敲核桃的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105006"]={id="guide105006",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="不过，此前仅剩的材料都用完了。阁主，且等我出去一趟，再带些回来。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guidechoice105007"]={id="guidechoice105007",bodyPos="",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我也一起去吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105008"]={id="guide105008",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主，您才醒来没多久……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105009"]={id="guide105009",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主都能铸剑了，下山一趟肯定也不成问题的！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105010"]={id="guide105010",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_angry,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="但还是要带上苒苒喔，实在出了什么状况，苒苒绝对能保护阁主。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide105011"]={id="guide105011",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="反正不能像以前那样，什么也不说就……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide106001"]={id="guide106001",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="呼……！闷在阁里这么久，终于能出去透口气啦。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide106002"]={id="guide106002",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="可我记得三天前你才下山买回了五串糖葫芦，还说买得少了，应该买十串才好。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide106003"]={id="guide106003",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哎呀哎呀…那个、材料都准备好了，阁主快去把锤子造出来吧……！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide107001"]={id="guide107001",bodyPos="1=100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="太多人了……根本忙不过来呀。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide107002"]={id="guide107002",bodyPos="2=101,100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="的确。阁主，若再不置办些便于造武器的地方，恐怕就没法应付那么多来客了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8001"]={id="guide8001",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="呀，碧影你看，怎么又是这人！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide8002"]={id="guide8002",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他可真有耐心，从三个月前算起，都来了五六回了吧？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8003"]={id="guide8003",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="100_look,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="每回都木愣愣的，光在门口一杵。我都说了好多次啦，阁主没醒，我们可给不起他要的东西……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8004"]={id="guide8004",bodyPos="1=-100,101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我去劝……不对不对，阁主这不是醒了吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8005"]={id="guide8005",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="几双眼睛忽然不约而同地盯了过来。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8006"]={id="guide8006",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="其实我还没有醒。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8007"]={id="guide8007",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苒苒学会锻铁了吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8008"]={id="guide8008",bodyPos="3=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗯哼哼，明白！让苒苒来……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8009"]={id="guide8009",bodyPos="3=100",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="当然！打铁和捏泥人不是差不多吗？只不过那些铁胚一敲就断，太不中用了！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8010"]={id="guide8010",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这位客人来了许多次，所求不过一件护甲。铁甲虽非贵重之物，却足见心意诚恳。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8011"]={id="guide8011",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主若有意做下这笔买卖，即便不记得锻造方法，但也不是全无出路。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8012"]={id="guide8012",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="武陵山中有一座村落，名唤甘泉村。阁主曾说，往年闹山贼时，你与老阁主在村中停留两月，为村民置办过许多兵械。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8013"]={id="guide8013",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="如今村落还在，关于那些往事，村民或还能说上一二。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8014"]={id="guide8014",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="甘泉村的一位大叔接待了我们。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="black",effect="",},
["guide8015"]={id="guide8015",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="提起这件事，他比比划划地谈起了往事，看来仍记忆犹新。说到那时的老阁主以纱蒙面，虽不以真面目示人，但谈吐温和；而阁主呢……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_yewaihu",effect="",},
["guide8016"]={id="guide8016",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哈哈，阁主是个才这么高的娃娃，大伙都说，这么个孩子都会做铁匠了！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8017"]={id="guide8017",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="可是做得确实不赖，后来老阁主就在这山上住下了，咱们才知道，这世上还有“铸剑阁”一说。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8018"]={id="guide8018",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="说到铁甲么，当年为了对付那伙山贼，我们巡逻的是人手一件，好几十年都还能穿呢。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8019"]={id="guide8019",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="老阁主讲的锻铁造甲的方法，我就学了个皮毛，打打下手还凑合。您想听，我就说说看。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8020"]={id="guide8020",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="对了，还有件事儿！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8021"]={id="guide8021",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="昨天夜里，还有位穿红衣的小哥来村子落脚，急匆匆的说是要去铸剑阁呢。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8022"]={id="guide8022",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="红衣……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide8023"]={id="guide8023",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苦思冥想一番，脑海里虽隐隐约约地有了这么个影子，却着实捉摸不透。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide8024"]={id="guide8024",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗐，您别急，照我看哪，这会他也该到了，您回去准能见上！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13012"]={id="guide13012",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_angry",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主！！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide13013"]={id="guide13013",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="来人声如洪钟，震得两侧的桌椅都似乎跳了跳。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13014"]={id="guide13014",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_think",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哎呀！阁主真醒了！我去山下一来一回，也就两天的功夫，怎么就偏偏不在……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide13015"]={id="guide13015",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_think",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哎，阁主记忆的事情，苒苒都给我讲了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13016"]={id="guide13016",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他低头想了想，大大咧咧地拍了拍胸膛，重新露出笑容。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13017"]={id="guide13017",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这有刚从炉子上端下来的烤兔腿、清炖羊汤和小馄饨，我荆高手做的饭，这十里八里都能闻到香！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide13018"]={id="guide13018",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="咱们重新认识一下。阁主，十年不见，来一份？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13019"]={id="guide13019",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哎哟，这就是铸剑阁哪，百闻不如一见……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="",},
["guide13020"]={id="guide13020",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主！看见您精神头这么好，我也放心了！不说了，险些把正事儿都忘光啦！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13021"]={id="guide13021",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我在家里翻了半天，找出这份手记。想着您用得上，就赶忙送上来了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide13022"]={id="guide13022",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="咱们武陵山上住的村民，大多都受过铸剑阁的恩。小事儿一桩，您不用记在心上。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24001"]={id="guide24001",bodyPos="3=1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_think",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哎，你是谁啊？怎么进来的？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="talkScene1",effect="",},
["guide24002"]={id="guide24002",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="刚拐过一个弯，就看见荆高手站在围墙下，他手里抓着把扫帚，正和一位不速之客面面相觑。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24003"]={id="guide24003",bodyPos="1=1041,704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,104_think",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这位客人，咱们这儿还没开张呢，你要是买东西，就请在外面等等。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24004"]={id="guide24004",bodyPos="2=704,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="不中嘞……俺家姑娘还等着吃饭，他们都说这山上有仙人……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24005"]={id="guide24005",bodyPos="1=1041,704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你说啥？什么仙人？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24006"]={id="guide24006",bodyPos="2=704,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="说灵得很，心想事成，仙人哪，俺别的不要，就要一斤白米！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24007"]={id="guide24007",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那人一转眼，瞧见了你，忽然大呼小叫了起来。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24008"]={id="guide24008",bodyPos="2=704,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这位大仙俺见过的，好多年啦，还长得和以前那会一模一样！那时候，您教过俺一点手艺，俺别的不会，就裁缝做得特别精！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24009"]={id="guide24009",bodyPos="2=704,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="您说好好学，今后就能养活自己……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24010"]={id="guide24010",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他从包袱里抖出一件东西，赫然是件缝制完整的皮甲。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24011"]={id="guide24011",bodyPos="2=704,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这是仙人您当年赐下的，好多年啦，再怎么着也舍不得卖的。可我只有它能换粮食了……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24012"]={id="guide24012",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这衣甲上的一针一线，触感皆是熟悉无比，这一瞬间，好像当初缝制它的过程，仍历历在目。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24013"]={id="guide24013",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那时在自己身边学艺的青年如今已长大了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24014"]={id="guide24014",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我和你交换此物。小荆，你带他去领些米面吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide24015"]={id="guide24015",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那村民千恩万谢地走了。有了这件皮甲，摹其形再制新品，应当不是难题。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide24016"]={id="guide24016",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="或许曾做过的事，无论过了多久,仍会以某种形式再度为自己所认识。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31001"]={id="guide31001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……说到近日，山脚下来了个方士，声称自己极擅丹术，鼓动村民来他那儿买丹药，说吃了能防百病。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="talkScene1",effect="",},
["guide31002"]={id="guide31002",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这丹药我也买了一颗，云天，你瞅瞅看？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31003"]={id="guide31003",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他取了个匣子出来，在众人面前打开，里边有颗玲珑清香的紫丸，看起来还挺像那么回事的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31004"]={id="guide31004",bodyPos="1=104,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="他们都说这药吃了真有用，吃了夜里不咳、腰腿不酸，精神都好了，一颗还只要九十八钱。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31005"]={id="guide31005",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="叶云天接过，轻轻嗅了嗅。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31006"]={id="guide31006",bodyPos="2=102,1041",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你可以试试。甘草、茯苓等物掺了蜜调的蜜丸，虽然没什么用，但味道应当不错。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31007"]={id="guide31007",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31008"]={id="guide31008",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="104_think,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我可不是苒苒那啥都吃的小丫头，这东西要让她见着了，横竖得往嘴里塞。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31009"]={id="guide31009",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="104_think,0,0",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这东西不坏就好，万一把人吃出事了，那可是个大问题。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31010"]={id="guide31010",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="咱们几个人学这炼丹术，都是好些年的事了，云天是真学会了，我呢，学了就忘；苒苒只会搓丸子，碧影做出来的药有酸有苦……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31011"]={id="guide31011",bodyPos="1=1041,102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阁主，你还记得炼丹的事么？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31012"]={id="guide31012",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="还记得一点。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide31013"]={id="guide31013",bodyPos="3=104",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="啊？还记得什么？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31014"]={id="guide31014",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="面对他们突然炽热起来的眼神，后面这句话忽然变得有些难以说出口……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31015"]={id="guide31015",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="记得阁里有座丹炉。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide31016"]={id="guide31016",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="那丹炉个头挺大的，立在山上，想看不见都难。好像以前，有个人也常常在炉旁教我辨认草药。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31017"]={id="guide31017",bodyPos="3=102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我们一起去看看吧。有问题，可以问我。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide31018"]={id="guide31018",bodyPos="3=102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……能多想起一点，也是好的。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide10001"]={id="guide10001",bodyPos="3=102",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{147,-100}},modelldScale={60,60,85},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="苒苒带的信，到得尚算及时。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="talkScene1",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide10002"]={id="guide10002",bodyPos="2=101,-102",offset={{147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="你回来得正是时候。这趟外出游历，可有什么收获？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide10003"]={id="guide10003",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="听见了一些传闻。不过，晚些再说亦不迟。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide10004"]={id="guide10004",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="此人拄枪而立，腰背挺拔，自然流露出英悍之气，似是武者出身。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide10005"]={id="guide10005",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="重要的是……你醒了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide10006"]={id="guide10006",bodyPos="2=101,-102",offset={{147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="云天自幼长于阁中，与诸位皆为手足之交，如今他回到阁中，必能成为阁主的助力。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide10007"]={id="guide10007",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我来晚了。阁主失忆一事，先前我已得知。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide10008"]={id="guide10008",bodyPos="1=-102,101",offset={{147,-100},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={85,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="无论如何，你便是你。阁主与我们之间的情谊，并不会有所改变。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11001"]={id="guide11001",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="有人在么？这儿有笔送上门的生意，沙曼城买来的宝贝，您瞧一瞧看一看啊！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="talkScene1",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["guide11002"]={id="guide11002",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="来人笑眯眯地从怀里摸出一只布袋，珍而重之地打开。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11003"]={id="guide11003",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="打开一层，复有一层，最后一个袋子里掉出了一张巴掌大的折纸。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11004"]={id="guide11004",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这是……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide11005"]={id="guide11005",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="听说铸剑阁开门了，这张如假包换的珍品设计，您肯定有兴趣！来头可大着呢！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11006"]={id="guide11006",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="沙曼城女王即位大典上，就戴着这么一整套首饰，那叫什么，琳琅满目，珠光宝气！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11007"]={id="guide11007",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="定睛一看，这上头的绘画好似……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11008"]={id="guide11008",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这些纵横深浅的划痕……根本不是首饰吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide11009"]={id="guide11009",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="嗨，您别见怪，那就是拿错了，我重说一遍！这张符箓啊，是一位道行高深的大师花了十年功夫才画成的，图案镇宅驱邪，招财进宝，心想事成，要啥有啥！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11010"]={id="guide11010",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="两万通宝，底价，您就说要不要吧！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11011"]={id="guide11011",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……不要。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["guide11012"]={id="guide11012",bodyPos="3=704",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="什么人哪，不识货。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11013"]={id="guide11013",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="兴许是拒绝得太干脆，来人脸色一板，满脸谄笑消失得一干二净，转身便走。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11014"]={id="guide11014",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="走得却也利落，只不过，地上好像掉下了什么东西……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["guide11015"]={id="guide11015",bodyPos="0=999",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,65},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="……两万通宝，不要紧吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,playerName",},
["level501001"]={id="level501001",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="燃烧的废墟之间，镇中居民俱是形色匆忙，或奔走救火，或忙于搬开倾颓的焦木砖瓦。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501002"]={id="level501002",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="盛景成灰，弦断声咽，谣音镇中充斥着无尽的哭泣与悲号，再也不复初见时的景象。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501003"]={id="level501003",bodyPos="1=10007,102",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="阿桃她没有和大家一起回来，是吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501004"]={id="level501004",bodyPos="2=102,10007",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="谷主并未受伤，不过……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501005"]={id="level501005",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="念及玉叶谷似有复杂的隐情，叶云天不免略作迟疑。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501006"]={id="level501006",bodyPos="1=10007,102",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="这样……没关系，重鹤未曾回来，我便明白了。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501007"]={id="level501007",bodyPos="1=10007,102",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="早在修成人形之前，我就能听见外界的声音。大家都会来到山后，在无人处倾诉心声……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501008"]={id="level501008",bodyPos="1=10007,102",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（那时，重鹤也曾经……）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501009"]={id="level501009",bodyPos="1=10007,102",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="重鹤所思所想，远比表面更为激烈，注定与玉叶谷有决裂的那天。他不会伤害阿桃，却不惮于伤害无辜的人。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501010"]={id="level501010",bodyPos="1=10007,102",offset={{0,-140},{147,-100},{0,0}},modelldScale={70,85,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="此间事了，我会回到玉叶谷，将发生的事告知谷中人，想办法将阿桃带回。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501011"]={id="level501011",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="幻魇纱亦落入重鹤之手，镇主打算如何处置？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501012"]={id="level501012",bodyPos="3=1171",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,117_sad",npcImageColor="",content_langId="鹿茵跪伏在地，喃喃自语，竟仿佛未曾听清身侧的交谈。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501013"]={id="level501013",bodyPos="3=1171",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="0,0,117_sad",npcImageColor="",content_langId="谣音镇……在这场变故中，失去了太多的人……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501014"]={id="level501014",bodyPos="1=10007,1171",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="盘踞不散的悲伤，回荡在耳中，就像永不停歇的浪潮。你的、我的、生者的、死者的……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501015"]={id="level501015",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="远处不知是谁高喊了一声：“下雨了——！”",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501016"]={id="level501016",bodyPos="-1",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="随着这一声惊呼，凝聚在头顶的沉沉阴云，终于以磅礴之势下起了大雨。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501017"]={id="level501017",bodyPos="3=1171",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="守护幻魇纱与谣音镇，乃是鹿蜀一族的使命。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501018"]={id="level501018",bodyPos="3=1171",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="鹿茵代谣音镇生灵恳请阁主相助，唯有夺回幻魇纱，谣音镇方能维持和平……",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501019"]={id="level501019",bodyPos="3=101",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="幻魇纱下落不明，此计难以急于一时。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["level501020"]={id="level501020",bodyPos="3=1171",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="不……我知道，它在哪里。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_001"]={id="gift_laozheng_001",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="得以在此巧遇阁主，不失为一桩缘分。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="bg_yewaihu",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_002"]={id="gift_laozheng_002",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我叫做郑峰。郑家开有一座林场，就在此处附近。先父与老阁主素有交情，本为铸剑阁供应木材，不过自闭阁以来，此事早已搁置。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_003"]={id="gift_laozheng_003",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="今后阁主如有需要，郑家定会为您寻来最上等的的良材……此外，还望阁主能够听我一言。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_004"]={id="gift_laozheng_004",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我等育得良木，倍加珍惜，可惜若无巧匠，良材也不过是一块无用的木头。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_005"]={id="gift_laozheng_005",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="当年黑潮之战时动荡不安，郑家所传木刻技艺就此尘封，再无后人能现其风采。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_006"]={id="gift_laozheng_006",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="如今阁主出面，若能以郑家良木，造出传世之珍品，岂不是快事？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_laozheng_007"]={id="gift_laozheng_007",bodyPos="3=6",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我身无长物，平生唯此一件心事，便是挂怀林场与木材。这张图纸，便赠予阁主，但愿能得您相助。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_rendong_001"]={id="gift_rendong_001",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="有……有人在吗？",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["gift_rendong_002"]={id="gift_rendong_002",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="来之前，镇主姐姐可没说过铸剑阁这么远呀……要是没人在可怎么办？呀，你是从哪儿突然冒出来的！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？|6",},
["gift_rendong_003"]={id="gift_rendong_003",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我明白了，你就是铸剑阁的阁主，对不对？姐姐都教过我了，见了主人要问好，要自报家门！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_rendong_004"]={id="gift_rendong_004",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="咳嗯，我代谣音镇所有妖族，向阁主问好……嗯，我叫忍冬，受谣音镇主所托送来薄礼，祝贺铸剑阁重开之时广迎八方来客，热闹兴隆。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,忍冬",},
["gift_rendong_005"]={id="gift_rendong_005",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="（呼……顺利说完了，没有错误！再接再厉！）",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,忍冬",},
["gift_rendong_006"]={id="gift_rendong_006",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="您是云麓的大英雄，愿鹿神庇佑您平安顺遂。我们谣音镇虽是妖族一脉，但素来与铸剑阁立场一致，都希望每位人族妖族，能够和和睦睦、平安快乐地生活在一起。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,忍冬",},
["gift_rendong_007"]={id="gift_rendong_007",bodyPos="3=703",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="所以、所以……若是需要帮忙，谣音镇一定会为阁主路见不平、拔刀相助！这份礼物，就请您收下吧！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,忍冬",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_001"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_001",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="一路从山脚上来，风景果真是满目苍翠，叫人心旷神怡哪。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_002"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_002",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="就是这选址也忒偏了些，要是客人腿脚不便，岂不是十分难办？阁主不如听我一言，将铸剑阁搬至镐梁城中，我的美人布坊隔壁，正有个人气兴旺的铺面呢。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_003"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_003",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="呵呵……美人布坊，既有绫罗绸缎、皮草兽绒，亦有美人。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_004"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_004",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="奴家名叫萧美人，是这皇都镐梁城中，数一数二的布坊掌柜。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_005"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_005",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="做生意讲究个人情往来，咱们都是商人，指不定哪一日，您还有能用得上我萧美人的地方呢。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_006"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_006",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="难得来阁中走一趟，奴家自然也备了一份薄礼。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_xiaomeiren_007"]={id="gift_xiaomeiren_007",bodyPos="3=11",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="铸剑阁……还真是让人好奇呢。若您有意，就多为奴家指点指点经商之道吧。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_biyushan_001"]={id="gift_biyushan_001",bodyPos="3=9",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="哈哈，你们大朔人有句俗话，叫做百闻不如一见，今日不远千里前来，果然不让人失望啊。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="**",effect="8,1,？？？",},
["gift_biyushan_002"]={id="gift_biyushan_002",bodyPos="3=9",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="我阿胡拉也算是沙曼城中有名有姓的大商人，铸剑阁重见天日，可不能白白错过了这等商机。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_biyushan_003"]={id="gift_biyushan_003",bodyPos="3=9",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="玉矿、金银，凡是珠宝用料，我们沙曼城都有最好的。若是能得到阁主慧眼相识，咱们的首饰行，肯定能更进一步。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_biyushan_004"]={id="gift_biyushan_004",bodyPos="3=9",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="倘若阁主愿意与我们合作，这些好东西，要多少有多少。",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},
["gift_biyushan_005"]={id="gift_biyushan_005",bodyPos="3=9",offset={{0,0},{0,0},{0,0}},modelldScale={60,60,60},bodyAniList={},expression="",npcImageColor="",content_langId="些许小礼，不成敬意，不成敬意！阁主可别忙着推辞，阿胡拉恭候您的答复，哈哈哈！",voiceId="",bgmId="",voiceEffectId={},talkBg="",effect="",},

}
